@mod @mod_quizinvideo
Feature: Edit quizinvideo page - delete
  In order to change the layout of a quizinvideo I built
  As a teacher
  I need to be able to delete questions.

  Background:
    Given the following "users" exist:
      | username | firstname | lastname | email               |
      | teacher1 | T1        | Teacher1 | teacher1@moodle.com |
    And the following "courses" exist:
      | fullname | shortname | category |
      | Course 1 | C1        | 0        |
    And the following "course enrolments" exist:
      | user     | course | role           |
      | teacher1 | C1     | editingteacher |
    And the following "activities" exist:
      | activity   | name   | course | idnumber |
      | quizinvideo       | quizinvideo 1 | C1     | quizinvideo1    |
    And I log in as "teacher1"
    And I follow "Course 1"

  @javascript
  Scenario: Delete questions by clicking on the delete icon.
    And I add a "True/False" question to the "quizinvideo 1" quizinvideo with:
      | Question name | Question A |
      | Question text | Answer me  |
    And I add a "True/False" question to the "quizinvideo 1" quizinvideo with:
      | Question name | Question B   |
      | Question text | Answer again |
    And I add a "True/False" question to the "quizinvideo 1" quizinvideo with:
      | Question name | Question C |
      | Question text | And again  |
    And I click on the "Add" page break icon after question "Question B"

    # Confirm the starting point.
    Then I should see "Question A" on quizinvideo page "1"
    And I should see "Question B" on quizinvideo page "1"
    And I should see "Question C" on quizinvideo page "2"
    And I should see "Total of marks: 3.00"
    And I should see "Questions: 3"
    And I should see "This quizinvideo is open"

    # Delete last question in last page. Page contains multiple questions
    When I delete "Question C" in the quizinvideo by clicking the delete icon
    Then I should see "Question A" on quizinvideo page "1"
    And I should see "Question B" on quizinvideo page "1"
    And I should not see "Question C" on quizinvideo page "2"
    And I should see "Total of marks: 2.00"
    And I should see "Questions: 2"

    # Delete last question in last page. The page contains multiple questions and there are multiple pages.
    When I click on the "Add" page break icon after question "Question A"
    Then I should see "Question B" on quizinvideo page "2"
    And the "Remove" page break icon after question "Question A" should exist
    And I delete "Question B" in the quizinvideo by clicking the delete icon
    Then I should see "Question A" on quizinvideo page "1"
    And I should not see "Page 2"
    And I should not see "Question B" on quizinvideo page "2"
    And the "Remove" page break icon after question "Question A" should not exist
    And I should see "Total of marks: 1.00"

    # Delete last remaining question in the last remaining page.
    And I delete "Question A" in the quizinvideo by clicking the delete icon
    Then I should not see "Question A" on quizinvideo page "1"
    And I should not see "Page 1"
    And I should see "Total of marks: 0.00"

  @javascript @edit_quizinvideo_delete_start
  Scenario: Delete questions from the start of the list.
    # Add more questions.
    When I add a "Description" question to the "quizinvideo 1" quizinvideo with:
    | Question name | Question A |
    | Question text | Answer A   |

    And I add a "True/False" question to the "quizinvideo 1" quizinvideo with:
    | Question name | Question B |
    | Question text | Answer B   |

    And I add a "Description" question to the "quizinvideo 1" quizinvideo with:
    | Question name | Question C |
    | Question text | Answer C   |

    And I add a "True/False" question to the "quizinvideo 1" quizinvideo with:
    | Question name | Question D |
    | Question text | Answer D   |

    And I add a "True/False" question to the "quizinvideo 1" quizinvideo with:
    | Question name | Question E |
    | Question text | Answer E   |

    Then "Question A" should have number "i" on the edit quizinvideo page
    And "Question B" should have number "1" on the edit quizinvideo page
    And "Question C" should have number "i" on the edit quizinvideo page
    And "Question D" should have number "2" on the edit quizinvideo page
    And "Question E" should have number "3" on the edit quizinvideo page

    # Delete from first question in the last remaining page. Are the page breaks updated?
    When I delete "Question A" in the quizinvideo by clicking the delete icon
    Then "Question B" should have number "1" on the edit quizinvideo page
    And "Question C" should have number "i" on the edit quizinvideo page
    And "Question D" should have number "2" on the edit quizinvideo page
    And "Question E" should have number "3" on the edit quizinvideo page

    When I click on the "Add" page break icon after question "Question C"
    Then I should see "Page 1"
    And I should see "Question B" on quizinvideo page "1"
    And I should see "Question C" on quizinvideo page "1"
    Then I should see "Page 2"
    And I should see "Question D" on quizinvideo page "2"
    And I should see "Question E" on quizinvideo page "2"

    # Test reorder of pages
    When I click on the "Add" page break icon after question "Question B"
    Then I should see "Page 1"
    And I should see "Question B" on quizinvideo page "1"
    Then I should see "Page 2"
    And I should see "Question C" on quizinvideo page "2"
    Then I should see "Page 3"
    And I should see "Question D" on quizinvideo page "3"
    And I should see "Question E" on quizinvideo page "3"
